@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nqvshz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.87) / (v2 + 0.87 - tmp + 0.34)))
    v1 = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = ((v1 * (tmp + 0.01 / tmp + 0.24)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.41) - (v0 + 0.57 + v2 + 0.41)))
    tmp = (v1 * wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
